### Pengujian Titik Akhir API Modul Pelaporan Keuangan
### PENTING:
###   - Ganti {{token}} dengan token JWT dari hasil login
###   - Ganti {{accountId}} dengan UUID akun dari response GET /api/v1/accounts
###   - Endpoint pelaporan HANYA bisa diakses oleh OWNER dan ADMIN
###   - Semua endpoint wajib menggunakan parameter startDate dan endDate (format: YYYY-MM-DD)

# 1. Jurnal Umum (General Journal)
# Menampilkan seluruh entri jurnal beserta baris debit/kredit dalam rentang waktu
# Akses: OWNER, ADMIN
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reports/general-journal?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJqaWthc2FAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzczMDI3MTkwLCJleHAiOjE3NzMxMTM1OTB9.TLcfDTBEnwtF6QA_3DbnMNs8sS2U-LDm-44hPkdcusA

###

# 2. Buku Besar (General Ledger) untuk Satu Akun Tertentu
# Menampilkan riwayat pergerakan satu akun dengan saldo berjalan (running balance)
# Akses: OWNER, ADMIN
# PENTING: Ganti {{accountId}} dengan UUID akun yang ingin dilihat (misal: akun Kas)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reports/general-ledger/f7443618-d1d7-4068-a4e0-10f163e5ea64?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJqaWthc2FAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzczMDI3MTkwLCJleHAiOjE3NzMxMTM1OTB9.TLcfDTBEnwtF6QA_3DbnMNs8sS2U-LDm-44hPkdcusA

###

# 3. Neraca Saldo (Trial Balance)
# Menampilkan ringkasan total Debit dan Kredit per akun untuk validasi keseimbangan
# Akses: OWNER, ADMIN
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reports/trial-balance?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJqaWthc2FAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzczMDI3MTkwLCJleHAiOjE3NzMxMTM1OTB9.TLcfDTBEnwtF6QA_3DbnMNs8sS2U-LDm-44hPkdcusA

###

# 4. Laba Rugi (Profit & Loss / Income Statement)
# Menghitung: Laba Bersih = Total Pendapatan (REVENUE) - Total Beban (EXPENSE)
# Akses: OWNER, ADMIN
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reports/profit-and-loss?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJqaWthc2FAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzczMDI3MTkwLCJleHAiOjE3NzMxMTM1OTB9.TLcfDTBEnwtF6QA_3DbnMNs8sS2U-LDm-44hPkdcusA

###

# 5. Neraca (Balance Sheet)
# Rumus: Aset = Liabilitas + Ekuitas
# Menampilkan posisi keuangan perusahaan pada periode tertentu
# Akses: OWNER, ADMIN
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reports/balance-sheet?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJqaWthc2FAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzczMDI3MTkwLCJleHAiOjE3NzMxMTM1OTB9.TLcfDTBEnwtF6QA_3DbnMNs8sS2U-LDm-44hPkdcusA

###

# 6. Arus Kas (Cash Flow)
# Memfilter pergerakan uang khusus pada akun Kas atau Bank
# Menghitung: Net Cash Flow = Total Kas Masuk - Total Kas Keluar
# Akses: OWNER, ADMIN
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reports/cash-flow?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJqaWthc2FAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzczMDI3MTkwLCJleHAiOjE3NzMxMTM1OTB9.TLcfDTBEnwtF6QA_3DbnMNs8sS2U-LDm-44hPkdcusA

###

# 7. Ekspor Laba Rugi (Format PDF)
# Menghasilkan fail (file) dokumen PDF berisi tabel Laba Rugi
# Akses: OWNER, ADMIN
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reports/profit-and-loss?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31&format=pdf
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJqaWthc2FAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzczMDI3MTkwLCJleHAiOjE3NzMxMTM1OTB9.TLcfDTBEnwtF6QA_3DbnMNs8sS2U-LDm-44hPkdcusA

###

# 8. Ekspor Laba Rugi (Format Excel)
# Menghasilkan fail (file) lembar kerja XLSX berisi tabel Laba Rugi
# Akses: OWNER, ADMIN
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reports/profit-and-loss?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31&format=excel
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJqaWthc2FAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzczMDI3MTkwLCJleHAiOjE3NzMxMTM1OTB9.TLcfDTBEnwtF6QA_3DbnMNs8sS2U-LDm-44hPkdcusA
